@api = http://127.0.0.1:3000
@token = REEMPLAZAR_CON_TOKEN_DE_LOGIN
@roomCode = REEMPLAZAR_CON_CODIGO

### Estado de API y PostgreSQL
GET {{api}}/api/health

### Login
POST {{api}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "correo": "admin@vocatest.pe",
  "contrasena": "REEMPLAZAR"
}

### Universidades públicas
GET {{api}}/api/db/universidades

### Preguntas dinámicas
GET {{api}}/api/db/test

### Usuarios (administrador)
GET {{api}}/api/db/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Salas del administrador/profesor
GET {{api}}/api/db/salas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear sala
POST {{api}}/api/db/salas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Evaluación 2026-1",
  "pin": "4826"
}

### Cerrar sala
PATCH {{api}}/api/db/salas/{{roomCode}}/estado
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "activa": false
}
